{"tid":1717100,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"透視中國緊急預警：香港即將強硬鎮壓反送中運動（包括互聯網審查及23條）","createTime":"2019-11-13T13:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:27:06.000Z","uid":202577,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee1510697c87834717320d5ed50e28f78d85c48","tid":1717100,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:46:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.sinoinsider.com/2019/11/%e7%b7%8a%e6%80%a5%e9%a0%90%e8%ad%a6%ef%bc%9a%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%8d%b3%e5%b0%87%e5%bc%b7%e7%a1%ac%e9%8e%ae%e5%a3%93%e5%8f%8d%e9%80%81%e4%b8%ad%e9%81%8b%e5%8b%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.sinoinsider.com%2F2019%2F11%2F%25e7%25b7%258a%25e6%2580%25a5%25e9%25a0%2590%25e8%25ad%25a6%25ef%25bc%259a%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%258d%25b3%25e5%25b0%2587%25e5%25bc%25b7%25e7%25a1%25ac%25e9%258e%25ae%25e5%25a3%2593%25e5%258f%258d%25e9%2580%2581%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e9%2581%258b%25e5%258b%2595%2F&d=jGmFyvXa%2BxCeqK61Wy4eyxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=12619bf2\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.sinoinsider.com/2019/11/%e7%b7%8a%e6%80%a5%e9%a0%90%e8%ad%a6%ef%bc%9a%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%8d%b3%e5%b0%87%e5%bc%b7%e7%a1%ac%e9%8e%ae%e5%a3%93%e5%8f%8d%e9%80%81%e4%b8%ad%e9%81%8b%e5%8b%95/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄：<br />\n<br />\n我們認為上述跡象和最近的其他事態發展表明，中共和香港政府可能計劃最早在香港時間2019年11月13日晚上將會大力鎮壓示威者。香港警方可以進行大規模逮捕，加大警察對示威者的暴行，更容易使用致命武器。香港政府可能會對互聯網進行審查，並推動《基本法》第二十三條的實施。<br />\n<br />\n 為了避免香港發生類似天安門式的鎮壓，各國政府必須立即公開譴責中共、香港政府和香港警察部隊在11月11日對示威者和市民的濫權和暴力。"},{"pid":"0de91c38c1e707cfa058af9672ce0d935b9611f4","tid":1717100,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:46:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a3822096614742d7f4e48f844f77c2d3c077768","tid":1717100,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5151b44b1c42907e2d3fab37e80ef7d80ebfd938","tid":1717100,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc